{"tid":1143123,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"【樓盤傳真】2019首個驗樓不合格入伙盤—龍譽","createTime":"2019-05-07T13:43:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-08T10:50:19.000Z","uid":9812,"like":20,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"0caa4ae964a910ffbcc54214abc57c66f97a8219","tid":1143123,"uid":9812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T13:43:13.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/p.outlook/videos/614397092409600/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fp.outlook%2Fvideos%2F614397092409600%2F&d=702bRGgXdrZysJ%2FhnUM8S5tjV1Wc7Scp8ABb8MCffMw%3D&h=553562c3\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/p.outlook/videos/614397092409600/</a><br />\n【排氣喉有個窿】 早幾年中資積極投地，項目逐一落成。近期入伙，有啟德新發展區的龍譽，發展商係央企背景嘅保利置業，龍譽係佢地首個香港項目，不過都成為今年，第一個成績「見紅」嘅入伙盤。詹SIR探頭出浴室窗，甚至發現排氣喉有個窿。 <br />\n<br />\n一千萬買五百呎，個地下斜既<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5GMVoH9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5GMVoH9.png&h=264b1621&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nD喉一係爆既一係漏既<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/p27tJG6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fp27tJG6.png&h=fbea0a40&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tf1yano.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ftf1yano.png&h=dc5a1469&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nD磚又成排都空心既<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZumeEfX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZumeEfX.png&h=3c93e972&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n個sink仲要你側身先洗到碗 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Xf7p1tg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXf7p1tg.png&h=fca433eb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">中資唔撚識起樓就咪撚起啦<br />\n買左果D真係恭喜晒</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3dc16d56258a3ec0d9cc5dc999165279f5034b2","tid":1143123,"uid":9812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T13:55:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76e75c1ede657afd209420597d6be5e97f33bd94","tid":1143123,"uid":75550,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T14:02:43.000Z","msg":"日出康城個堆呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"482f52d16ccc07c5478aafce2c721c9e25315170","tid":1143123,"uid":29093,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T14:04:58.000Z","msg":"是撚但啦,  啲人都係買嚟炒架啫"},{"pid":"bb3f127681e327fcbbef6a9e957c1ff5acbc9174","tid":1143123,"uid":24443,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T14:06:26.000Z","msg":"2雞尺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05d0fff68d5828aa25c54cfb72a1fd23de5a71f6","tid":1143123,"uid":9812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"76e75c1ede657afd209420597d6be5e97f33bd94","tid":1143123,"uid":75550,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T14:02:43.000Z","msg":"日出康城個堆呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T14:08:53.000Z","msg":"而家暫時睇好似中資果D起得特撚別差